<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4930364>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–11. Features of Chlorogomphus danhkyi sp. nov., holotype ♂ & paratype ♀. (1) head & thorax ♂; (2) head & thorax ♀; (3, 4), head ♂, frontal and dorsal view; (5, 6), head ♀, frontal and dorsal view; (7), accessory genitalia; (8, 9), vesica spermalis in lateral and ventral view; (10, 11), abdominal tip ♀, lateral and ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4930364/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4930368>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–19. Appendages and head of Chlorogomphus spp., ♂. (14, 15), appendages of C. danhkyi sp. nov.; (16, 17), appendages of C. piaoacensis; (18, 19), head of C. danhkyi sp. nov., holotype ♂ & paratype ♀, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4930368/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4930366>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–13. Habitus of Chlorogomphus danhkyi sp. nov. (12), holotype ♂ & (13), paratype ♀. Measurements in centim- eters." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4930366/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4930373>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26–28. Habitats and distribution of Chlorogomphus spp. (26, 27), Khe Ro; (28), distribution of C. danhkyi sp. nov. (yellow circle) and C. piaoacensis (red circle)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4930373/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

